# REST API

- Base path `/api/v1`. Resource-oriented, plural nouns: `/leads`, `/opportunities`,
  `/presales`, `/pricing`, `/proposals`, `/contracts`, `/services`, `/billing/invoices`,
  `/after-sales/novelties`, `/audit-log`.
- Verbs: GET (list/detail), POST (create / action sub-resource e.g.
  `/opportunities/{id}/send-to-presales`), PUT (update), no DELETE on business records
  (soft-delete via state).
- Status: 200 ok, 201 created, 400 validation, 401 unauth, 403 forbidden, 404 not found,
  409 conflict (duplicate/state). Return a consistent error shape `{code, message, details}`.
- Pagination on every list: `?page&limit` + `{items, total, page, limit}`. Filters as query
  params (estado, segmento, responsable_id, from, to).
- Auth: Bearer JWT. Guard every route; authorize with CASL (`@CheckAbility`). Default deny.
- Request/response are DTOs, documented with Swagger decorators. Never expose model internals.
